roi_popover.raw_text:
Return on InvestmentA 15-year payback multiplier. Projects cumulative earnings over a typical 15-year repayment window (starting salary grown at flat 3% annually) and divides by the program's 4-year published cost. Higher = better. Financing-agnostic — the loan slider doesn't move it.Source: College Scorecard✦Ask Gemma about this
        @keyframes popoverIn {
          from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-6px); }
          to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }
